<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 06:17:50 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>官方媒体称，中国共产党将于 7 月 15 日至 18 日举行重要的三中全会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-communist-party-hold-key-third-plenum-july-15-18-state-media-say-2024-06-27/</link><description>据新华社周四报道，中国共产党将于 7 月 15 日至 18 日举行拖延已久的三中全会。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 05:45:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-communist-party-hold-key-third-plenum-july-15-18-state-media-say-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>回收将成为应对欧盟稀土挑战的长期解决方案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/recycling-kick-long-term-solution-eu-rare-earths-challenge-2024-06-27/</link><description>欧盟公司正准备利用回收的巨大潜力，为欧盟的绿色转型提供关键的稀土，但需要一段时间才能有足够的旧电动汽车和风力涡轮机供应来进行处理。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 04:12:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/recycling-kick-long-term-solution-eu-rare-earths-challenge-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>将稀土从矿山转化为磁体的复杂性</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/complexity-transforming-rare-earths-mine-magnet-2024-06-27/</link><description>欧盟将努力实现旨在提高国内关键矿物产量并减少对中国依赖的新立法中有关稀土的雄心勃勃的目标。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 04:06:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/complexity-transforming-rare-earths-mine-magnet-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>在夺回稀土荣耀的竞赛中，欧洲未能实现矿产目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/race-regain-rare-earth-glory-europe-falls-short-mineral-goals-2024-06-27/</link><description>四十年前，法国大西洋沿岸的一家稀土加工厂是世界上最大的稀土加工厂之一，生产用于制造彩色电视、弧光灯和相机镜头的材料。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 04:04:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/race-regain-rare-earth-glory-europe-falls-short-mineral-goals-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，腾讯支持的 Shift Up IPO 定价可能处于上限</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/tencent-backed-shift-up-may-price-ipo-top-end-band-source-says-2024-06-27/</link><description>据知情人士透露，由中国腾讯支持的韩国游戏公司 Shift Up 计划将其首次公开募股定价在其定价范围的高端，并筹集 4,350 亿韩元（3.13 亿美元）。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 03:45:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/tencent-backed-shift-up-may-price-ipo-top-end-band-source-says-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市下跌，日元暴跌令市场保持干预警惕</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-27/</link><description>周四，由于对通胀的担忧，亚洲股市下跌，债券收益率飙升，而日元兑美元汇率跌破 160 美元，货币交易员准备迎接日本介入并稳定日元汇率。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 02:21:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>母公司香港交易所表示，伦敦金属交易所(LME)将香港视为全球仓库所在地</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/lme-eyes-hong-kong-potential-warehouse-location-hkex-ceo-says-2024-06-27/</link><description>伦敦金属交易所（LME）首席执行官周四表示，该交易所正在探索将香港列为 LME 仓库地点的可能性，因为该交易所希望加强其全球物流足迹。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 01:43:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/lme-eyes-hong-kong-potential-warehouse-location-hkex-ceo-says-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国将对进口欧盟甲苯胺启动反倾销复审</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-start-review-anti-dumping-measures-imports-eus-toluidine-2024-06-27/</link><description>中国商务部周四表示，中国将对进口欧盟甲苯胺（用于染料、药品和农药）启动反倾销期终复审。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 01:31:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-start-review-anti-dumping-measures-imports-eus-toluidine-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>美国、日本、韩国誓言开展战略合作以促进安全和经济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-japan-south-korea-vow-strategic-cooperation-boost-security-economies-2024-06-27/</link><description>美国、日本和韩国的商务和贸易部长周三誓言将在人工智能（AI）安全、出口管制、清洁能源和半导体供应链等战略问题上进行合作。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 00:57:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-japan-south-korea-vow-strategic-cooperation-boost-security-economies-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国为应对致命洪水的城市提供超过3.16亿美元的紧急救援</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-provides-additional-natural-disaster-relief-funds-says-state-media-2024-06-27/</link><description>由于近两周的暴雨肆虐中国多个地区，造成致命的洪水和山体滑坡，中国提供了超过23亿元人民币（3.164亿美元）的资金，以帮助救援工作、应急物资和规划。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 00:53:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-provides-additional-natural-disaster-relief-funds-says-state-media-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>由于干预风险迫在眉睫，日元陷入近十年低点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/battered-yen-pinned-near-multi-decade-low-amid-resilient-dollar-2024-06-27/</link><description>周四，日元跌至 38 年低点附近，并在 1 美元兑 160 日元的弱势区间徘徊，这让市场对日本当局采取干预措施支撑日元的任何迹象保持警惕。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 00:30:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/battered-yen-pinned-near-multi-decade-low-amid-resilient-dollar-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>早盘买盘：通胀恐慌和日元空头</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-26/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 21:51:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾大使没有在中国争端中寻求美国的补给支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-has-not-sought-us-resupply-support-china-dispute-ambassador-2024-06-26/</link><description>菲律宾驻华盛顿大使周三表示，在与中国在有争议的南中国海的对峙中，菲律宾尚未请求美国支持为其军队提供补给，并补充说美国只是提供援助菲律宾的“视觉”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 20:47:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-has-not-sought-us-resupply-support-china-dispute-ambassador-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，波音公司恢复向中国交付宽体飞机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-resuming-widebody-airplane-deliveries-china-source-says-2024-06-26/</link><description>据知情人士透露，波音公司正在恢复向中国供应宽体喷气式飞机，该项目最近几周因中国监管审查而暂停。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 20:24:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-resuming-widebody-airplane-deliveries-china-source-says-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>由于对中国进口产品征收更高关税，沃尔沃将推迟 EX30 在美国的发货</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-delay-ex30s-us-shipments-due-higher-tariffs-chinese-imports-bloomberg-news-2024-06-26/</link><description>沃尔沃汽车发言人周三表示，在中国出口关税上调后，沃尔沃汽车将推迟在美国交付 EX30 电动汽车，因为该公司专注于扩大中国以外紧凑型 SUV 的生产。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 19:14:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-delay-ex30s-us-shipments-due-higher-tariffs-chinese-imports-bloomberg-news-2024-06-26/</guid></item></channel></rss>